Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.45,0:00:45.44,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I look up to \Nthe sky after the rain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:51.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nakimushi datta koro no boku wo omou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:51.15,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I think back to when I was a crybaby
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:58.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,dareka no senaka wo gamushara ni oikaketa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.19,0:00:58.91,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I was chasing somebody's back blindly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.03,0:01:01.70,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"tsuyoku naritai" tte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.03,0:01:01.70,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking "I want to be stronger"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:07.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ima wa kaze ni kieta "arigatou"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:07.21,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The word "thank you" has \Nfaded into the wind now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.29,0:01:12.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,boku wa tsuyoku nareteiru no kana?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.29,0:01:12.38,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I getting stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.51,0:01:18.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,kotae wa mada desou ni nai kara sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.51,0:01:18.05,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know the answer yet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.09,0:01:23.39,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,yappari mada aruiteiku yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.09,0:01:23.39,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'll keep walking ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.64,0:01:25.81,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,saa yukou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.64,0:01:25.81,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:29.11,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,tachidomaru koto naku
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:29.11,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.23,0:01:34.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nagareru toki ni makenai youni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.23,0:01:34.44,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without giving up to the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:39.91,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nando mo tachimukai tsuzukeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.49,0:01:39.91,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep getting back up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.05,0:01:45.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,taisetsu na mono ushinaitakunai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.05,0:01:45.41,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to \Nlose something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:50.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,boku no naka ni nagareru koe wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.54,0:01:50.84,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,The voice inside of me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:56.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,zutto zutto boku wo sasaeteru
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:56.01,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,keeps sustaining me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:02:01.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,itazura na ame ga jama suru kedo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.17,0:02:01.26,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Wicked rain will get in my way
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:06.10,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nigedasanai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.39,0:02:06.10,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't walk away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:11.69,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,saa yukou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:11.69,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:14.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Tachidomaru koto naku
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:14.98,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without stopping
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:20.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nagareru toki ni makenai youni
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:20.16,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Without giving up to the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.28,0:02:25.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,nando mo tachimukai tsuzukeyou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.28,0:02:25.83,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep getting back up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:31.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,taisetsu na mono ushinaitakunai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:31.38,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to \Nlose something precious
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:39.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,shinjita sono saki e to...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:39.68,DefaultLow,,0000,0000,0000,,To the future I believe in...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is the Great Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Countless pirates fight \Ndesperately for the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:02:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the great treasure left behind by \NGold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.88,0:03:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned \Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.68,0:03:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,also takes to the sea to become \Nthe next King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.47,0:03:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Luffy and his friends \Novercome numerous adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the World Government is less and \Nless able to ignore their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of adventure \Nis waiting for us next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crew, on its way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will speed along the Grand Line again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.00,0:03:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Separated from the rest of the Straw Hats,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.20,0:03:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy made it to Marineford to rescue \Nhis brother, Ace who will be executed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.60,0:03:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He and the Whitebeards have invaded to \Nthe plaza to make it to the scaffold!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.96,0:03:52.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the midst of the Navy's onslaught, \Nwith the Whitebeards' assistance,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.33,0:03:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy ran on the path that Inazuma \Ncreated and finally made it to Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.46,0:04:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a remnant from the old times!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.43,0:04:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no ship that can \Nbear me in the new era!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.30,0:04:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get it over with!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.23,0:04:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Power That Can Burn Even \NFire! Akainu's Ruthless Pursuit!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.63,0:04:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Marineford is in danger!\N--Stop Whitebeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.21,0:04:40.84,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,ABSOLUTE JUSTICE
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.58,0:04:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's willing to destroy the whole island!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.31,0:04:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.30,0:04:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna leave you! \NYou gotta come with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.86,0:04:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.33,0:05:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you disobey your Captain's order?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.37,0:05:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you just go, fools?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.28,0:05:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now is our chance! Kill \NWhitebeard! He's dying already!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.05,0:05:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.30,0:05:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up! Let's do as Pops said!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.53,0:05:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't mind leaving Pops behind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:32.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, how dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.63,0:05:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid! No one wants to leave him alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.31,0:05:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.33,0:05:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grumbling about it at a time
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.81,0:05:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,like this is the same as trampling \Non Pops' determination!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.56,0:05:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.40,0:05:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.23,0:05:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and get ready to sail out!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.58,0:05:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.60,0:06:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna leave soon! Come on now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.52,0:06:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander Marco, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.11,0:06:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pops...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.28,0:06:36.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You messed with us!\N--Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.45,0:06:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait! All I want is to get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention to fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.59,0:06:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.76,0:06:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My wax is as strong as steel!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.30,0:06:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that a \Nnormal sword can cut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.30,0:06:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's also a Devil Fruit eater!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.81,0:06:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.30,0:06:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's strong enough to try to protect
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.04,0:07:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\N"Fire Fist" even at Fleet Admiral Sengoku's elbow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No no, don't overestimate me \Nlike that! I'm not a big deal...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.12,0:07:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn Whitebeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.29,0:07:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe he still has that much \Npower after getting wounded so badly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.30,0:07:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since he isn't concerned about \N"Fire Fist" Ace anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fleet Admiral Sengoku!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.89,0:07:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's clear his intention is to \Nsink Marineford into the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.60,0:07:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Along with himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.52,0:07:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Admiral Garp! You're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.28,0:07:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wants to change the era? \NYeah, the time is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:07:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Whitebeard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.99,0:08:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His allies who have been \Nsold out are all dead now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.25,0:08:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the connection still out?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long should we wait?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.85,0:08:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! We couldn't see the whole picture
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.50,0:08:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nbecause Buggy the Clown stood in our way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.89,0:08:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy over there must be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.81,0:08:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The great pirate--Captain Buggy the Clown?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.80,0:08:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's who I am indeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.82,0:08:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did he want to say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.73,0:08:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If nothing is done, I can't report \Nanything to the head office!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.41,0:08:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on at Marineford now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.66,0:08:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.37,0:08:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Transponder Snail hasn't come out yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.50,0:08:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Captain Buggy is about to beat \NWhitebeard - it's no time for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.05,0:08:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say it as if it's so easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.68,0:08:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's dying but he still has boundless \Npower - didn't they see it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.93,0:09:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did I even say that I'm gonna beat \Nthat man?! I really screwed this up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.18,0:09:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it! It's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.40,0:09:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! We gotta broadcast Captain \NBuggy's big moment all over the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get it out at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.28,0:09:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Come out now!\N--Or we're gonna burn you out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.66,0:09:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we gotta soak it into water!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.33,0:09:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Let's do that!\N--Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.25,0:09:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Stop it, fools!\N--Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.50,0:09:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like he volunteered \Nto be a slave for the Navy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.59,0:09:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he got beaten up in the \Nbattlefield like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.09,0:09:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you feel sorry for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.54,0:09:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just let him go, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.06,0:09:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we gotta cancel "Captain \NBuggy's beating beard
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.54,0:09:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and broadcast it live to the world" plan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.11,0:09:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Even you want to \Npull out from Marineford?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.61,0:09:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm disappointed in you, Captain Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.16,0:10:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.24,0:10:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes down to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.95,0:10:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they're all strong guys who've \Nbeen locked up in Impel Down!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.37,0:10:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I better not make enemies of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.68,0:10:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Transponder Snail came out voluntarily!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.46,0:10:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.64,0:10:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.22,0:10:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah! He came out because he was \Ntouched by Captain Buggy's kindness!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.76,0:10:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Buggy can even win \Nthe hearts of the Snails!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.51,0:10:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's amazing as we thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.98,0:10:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the man who will conquer \Nthe world - he's our Captain Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.78,0:10:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Damn bastard! Why didn't \Nhe just stay inside?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.95,0:10:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now there's no way that I can back out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.45,0:10:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, let's begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.70,0:10:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Buggy, make a declaration \Nto conquer the world now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.60,0:10:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's your moment!\N--Smoke: good, lighting: good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.46,0:10:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand by!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.13,0:11:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, I mean... Dammit! \NThis leaves me one choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, shoot my bravery!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.20,0:11:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Capture the moment that I kill Whitebeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.15,0:11:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey, look!\N--The picture's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.40,0:11:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't see what's going \Non because of the smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.11,0:11:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the Navy losing?! What \Nhappened to Whitebeard and Ace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.07,0:11:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Um, well...\N--Transponder Snail, go lower!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.46,0:11:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, everyone! I'm Buggy and I'm a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.61,0:11:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.80,0:11:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get to the sea now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.64,0:11:44.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We who remain have to go back \Nto the New World safely!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let them get away! \NKill as many as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.02,0:11:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only one that you \Nought to worry about!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.40,0:11:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander Jozu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.90,0:12:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like he's badly \Ninjured but he'll make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.65,0:12:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain gave us an order! Come with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.16,0:12:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brenheim! You gotta carry Jozu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.79,0:12:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw boy! Why are you standing around?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.96,0:12:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace, let's go! The old man \Nhas made up his mind...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.68,0:12:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! And it won't be in vain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back off, you bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.61,0:13:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need words now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.28,0:13:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just tell me one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.53,0:13:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you happy to have me as your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.76,0:13:49.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still some fight left in you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.43,0:13:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are too valuable to let die now, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.27,0:13:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you still wanna run wild, run as wild \Nas you want on the sea under my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.58,0:14:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Become my son!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.95,0:14:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.49,0:14:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.45,0:14:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--The scaffold was destroyed!\N--So was the Navy HQ!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.27,0:15:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Ace get executed?! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.49,0:15:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move the camera to Whitebeard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.33,0:15:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Buggy and I'm a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.55,0:15:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The great pirate--Captain Buggy the Clown!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.12,0:15:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true that you're \Ngonna beat Whitebeard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.77,0:15:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And with his head in your hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.87,0:15:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're willing to become \None of The Four Emperors?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.56,0:15:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Buggy and I'm a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.98,0:15:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just repeating that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.81,0:15:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say something forward-looking! \NLet's do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.69,0:15:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough with Buggy! Show us \NMarineford as it stands!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.70,0:15:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.82,0:15:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not what we're interested in!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.87,0:15:41.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I mean... I just wanna \Ndo something flashy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.41,0:15:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.09,0:15:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run! Run to the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.97,0:15:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ace-san, Luffy-kun, get in front of me!\N--Jimbei!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.01,0:15:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They want to get you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:16:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what the good old man wants \Nis as many survivors as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.27,0:16:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.56,0:16:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've stolen a Navy ship! Get on board quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.04,0:16:18.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do they really think that they can \Nget away?! How simple they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.09,0:16:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Admiral Sakazuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.79,0:16:24.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys, move aside a little bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.43,0:16:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two, just keep going \Nuntil you get to the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.93,0:16:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As soon as you rescue \N"Fire Fist" Ace, you run!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.50,0:16:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Whitebeards must be a group of cowards!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.27,0:16:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.40,0:16:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's trying to stir you up obviously!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.08,0:16:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you stop, you're playing into his hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.60,0:17:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well your captain is that guy \Nso you can't help it, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.47,0:17:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because after all, Whitebeard is just a...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.92,0:17:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...loser from the old times!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.00,0:17:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.68,0:17:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A loser?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.06,0:17:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take back what you just said!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.94,0:17:28.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't, Ace! Don't stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.96,0:17:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just let him say whatever he wants!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.69,0:17:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He mocked Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.28,0:17:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.40,0:17:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say "take it back?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.99,0:17:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not in a million years! I'll tell you why.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.28,0:17:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father Gold Roger \Nconquered the Grand Line
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.46,0:17:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and opened the door to the new era called
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.05,0:17:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nthe Great Pirate Era by sacrificing himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.85,0:17:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a Navy admiral, it's \Nnot my place to say so,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.42,0:18:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he was true to his name: \Nthe King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.10,0:18:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In contrast, what has Whitebeard done?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he really had \Nthe intention to fight .
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.94,0:18:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I assume that he established \Na large family someplace
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.30,0:18:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and was satisfied being a \Nbig fish in a little barrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.49,0:18:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are some fools in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.91,0:18:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who'd say that his name is \Nkeeping peace on various islands
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.70,0:18:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if you ask me, he's just keeping \Nlightweights in fear of him
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.70,0:18:34.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he thinks that he's a \Nhero which makes me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.20,0:18:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Roger was alive, \NWhitebeard had second billing
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.09,0:18:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and even after Roger's death, \Nhe couldn't become a King.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.85,0:18:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means he'll never better Roger \Nand he'll be a loser forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.06,0:18:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's who Whitebeard \Nis and that's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.19,0:18:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a poor man when you think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.89,0:18:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NHe gathered some punks who call him Pops
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.34,0:19:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and roamed around the sea \Nwith his fake family.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.37,0:19:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.45,0:19:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And although he reigned the sea for years,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.41,0:19:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he couldn't become a King and gained nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.50,0:19:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and at the end, he was stabbed by a fool,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.86,0:19:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\None of his sons who fell for my line
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.38,0:19:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he will die to protect that son.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.44,0:19:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think that his life is so empty?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.56,0:19:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.56,0:19:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it, Ace, come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.52,0:19:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.39,0:19:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pops gave us a place to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.69,0:19:43.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't understand his greatness!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.64,0:19:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People don't deserve to live \Nif they can't live justly!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.95,0:19:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Punks like you guys don't \Ndeserve a place to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.79,0:19:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.04,0:19:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whitebeard will die as a loser! It's \Nfitting for a big fish in a little barrel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.59,0:20:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whitebeard is a great pirate \Nwho shaped this era!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.85,0:20:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make fun of the man who saved me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.64,0:20:12.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.77,0:20:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The name of this era should be "Whitebeard!"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.12,0:20:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both Whitebeard and you \Nguys who call him Pops
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.78,0:20:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are the same after all--losers!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.96,0:20:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace has been burned!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.15,0:20:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you careless because you \Nate a Logia type fruit which
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.70,0:20:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is the most powerful of all?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.14,0:20:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just fire but my \Nmagma can even burn fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.44,0:21:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My power is far stronger than yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.57,0:21:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.04,0:21:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy-kun, you should not fight anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.88,0:21:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace's Vivre Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.96,0:21:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger the King of the Pirates, \NDragon--the revolutionary.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.52,0:21:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was amazed to hear that sons \Nof those two are step brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.55,0:21:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two have bad blood in your veins.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.67,0:21:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if the others get \Naway as long as I get you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.06,0:21:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch what I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.86,0:21:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.55,0:21:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.26,0:22:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is certainly a Vivre Card.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.17,0:22:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I haven't told you that this card
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.29,0:22:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,also tells you how much \Nvital energy the owner has.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.14,0:22:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card belongs to someone \Nwho you care for, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.93,0:22:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's my brother's!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.82,0:22:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold onto it, always.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.00,0:23:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That paper will lead us to one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.45,0:23:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace is pierced by Akainu's \Nfist while protecting Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.71,0:23:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimbei and the Whitebeard \NPirates try to save him,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.51,0:23:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Ace, realizing he is about to die,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.96,0:23:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,finds the voice to convey his feelings \Nto his friends one last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.73,0:23:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.19,0:23:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Looking for the Answer! Fire Fist Ace \NDies on the Battlefield!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.98,0:23:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!
